dct_title_s: Burlington County Farmlands, New Jersey1980 - Northern half
dct_description_sm: Northern half of a map commissioned by the U. S. Department of Agriculture Soil Conservation Service showing all areas of important farmland in Burlington County. Water and urban areas are also shown. Map includes an explanation of the soil survey process used to determine the different topographic features.
